    (fun x => (pdf X ‚Ñô Œº x).toReal) =·µê[Œº] fun x => (s.indicator ((Œº s)‚Åª¬π ‚Ä¢ (1 : E ‚Üí ‚Ñù‚â•0‚àû)) x).toReal :=
  Filter.EventuallyEq.fun_comp hX Ennreal.toReal

theorem measure_preimage {m : MeasurableSpace Œ©} {X : Œ© ‚Üí E} {‚Ñô : Measure Œ©} {Œº : Measure E} {s : Set E} (hns : Œº s ‚â† 0)
    (hnt : Œº s ‚â† ‚àû) (hms : MeasurableSet s) (hu : IsUniform X s ‚Ñô Œº) {A : Set E} (hA : MeasurableSet A) :
    ‚Ñô (X ‚Åª¬π' A) = Œº (s ‚à© A) / Œº s := by
  haveI := hu.has_pdf hns hnt
  rw [‚Üê measure.map_apply (has_pdf.measurable X ‚Ñô Œº) hA, map_eq_set_lintegral_pdf X ‚Ñô Œº hA,
    lintegral_congr_ae hu.restrict]
  simp only [hms, hA, lintegral_indicator, Pi.smul_apply, Pi.one_apply, Algebra.id.smul_eq_mul, mul_one‚Çì,
    lintegral_const, restrict_apply', Set.univ_inter]
  rw [Ennreal.div_eq_inv_mul]

theorem is_probability_measure {m : MeasurableSpace Œ©} {X : Œ© ‚Üí E} {‚Ñô : Measure Œ©} {Œº : Measure E} {s : Set E}
    (hns : Œº s ‚â† 0) (hnt : Œº s ‚â† ‚àû) (hms : MeasurableSet s) (hu : IsUniform X s ‚Ñô Œº) : IsProbabilityMeasure ‚Ñô :=
  ‚ü®by
